only point that needs to be set to operate the cartridge hotel. Set as grasp of topleft cartridge, make sure all cartridges are reachable. This relies on the fact that the coordinate system of this point is set properly (thus +120 is next vertical cartidge in Z-axis and -65 is the next cartridge horizontally must be X-axis. This will require fiddling and should take some time to get right. My approach is to first optimize alpha with binary search by hand untill the grasp on the furthest horizontally cartridge is perfect. After that I will do the same for the bottom left cartridge with Beta. When those 2 furthest are grasping nicely, only then I will try the bottomright cartridge, and this should be considered a final test, do not try to optimise coordinate system for this point directly - but use the approach outlined.
